	(raptor_format_float): use a long for the intpart.

	* configure.ac:
	Expand (GCC) compiler warnings lots

	* docs/raptor-1-to-2-map.tsv, docs/raptor-sections.txt,
	src/raptor2.h.in, src/raptor_internal.h,
